[23/04/2017 01:42:39] <font color="#00ff00">Pero no le hablo al abogado,</font>
[23/04/2017 01:42:42] <font color="#00ff00">sino a la persona, a su lado humano.</font>
[23/04/2017 01:42:45] <font color="#00ff00">Yo no fui.</font>
[23/04/2017 01:42:48] <font color="#00ff00">No maté a mi marido.</font>
[23/04/2017 01:42:51] <font color="#0000ff">(Música suave)</font>
[23/04/2017 01:42:56] <font color="#00ff00">Ah...</font>
